<title>Previo a la unidad</title>
<!-- <title>Exploración</title> -->
<!-- <title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="graVV-uniYY-secZZ" text="title"/></title> -->
<!-- <title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-VVVVVV" text="title"/></title> -->

<statement>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151727">
    <shortdescription>Number line. First tick mark 0, last tick mark 100. 9 unlabeled tick marks between 0 and 100.</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <p>Escribe el número que corresponde debajo de cada marca de la recta numérica.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Ubica y marca 45 y 62 en la recta numérica.</p>
    </li>
  </ol>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-152485">
        <shortdescription>Number line.</shortdescription>
      </image>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Students do not need to plot the exact location of the numbers, but 45 should be between 40 and 50 and 62 should be between 60 and 70.</p>
      <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-152486">
        <shortdescription>Number line. 0 to 100 by tens. Evenly spaced tick marks. First tick mark, 0. Last tick mark, 100. Points plotted at 45 and 62.</shortdescription>
      </image>
    </li>
  </ol>
</solution>

</exercise>
